Kia EV3 är nu beställningsbar och kommer med två olika batteristorlekar. Standard Range med 58,3 kWh och en räckvidd på 436 km och Long Range 81,4 kWh som ger en räckvidd på upp till 605 km (WLTP).

Dessutom kommer EV3 med eftertraktade Plug & Charge, som gör laddstoppen enklare än någonsin. Upplev snabb och sömlös laddning från 10 till 80 procent på ner till 31 minuter. Men det slutar inte där. I allt från materialval till säkerhetssystem och drivlina visar Kia EV3 att det är en komplett bil, designad för alla resor.

cars.heading: Ferrari 599 GTB HGTE
cars.description:
This Ferrari 599 GTB was sold new in Italy by authorised Ferrari dealership Radicci Automobil. The car was delivered in a stunning Nero Daytona exterior, beautifully complemented by a Nero leather-trimmed cabin complete with white stitching, Cavallino-embroidered headrests, and extensive carbon-fibre trim. 

The car came equipped with equipment including front and rear parking sensors, automatic Xenon headlights, switchable drive modes via the Manettino dial, steering wheel?with?LED shift lights and carbon-fibre paddles, electrically adjustable sports seats with three-position driver’s memory, dual-zone climate control, and a Ferrari-branded Becker stereo with voice control and satellite navigation.

The car remained in Italy for its first few years, regularly serviced at the original dealership, before being imported to Germany and, to Sweden. Upon its arrival in Sweden, the authorised Ferrari dealer Autoropa retrofitted the car with the HGTE package (Handling Gran Turismo Evoluzione). This upgrade included both aesthetic and performance enhancements.

As part of the handling improvements, the stock wheels were replaced with lighter, three-piece forged units fitted with grippier tires to enhance traction. Aesthetically, the HGTE package introduced a redesigned chromatic grille and burnished Prancing Horse emblems. Completing the package were an enhanced exhaust system and a suite of performance upgrades. The F1 gearbox actuation was improved, reducing shift times to an impressive 85 milliseconds. The throttle response was also remapped for sharper performance. The exhaust system received new silencers and two-tone finished tailpipes, further elevating the car’s aggressive styling.

Since 2016, the 599 has been regularly serviced and maintained by EB Auto, a trusted MOTIKON partner and specialist in Italian sports cars. In 2021, a close friend of MOTIKON acquired the vehicle, with EB Auto continuing its dedicated care and maintenance. To ensure the car met the flawless standards MOTIKON strives for, a full overhaul and service were conducted in late 2023. This comprehensive work, documented with invoices totaling 176, included replacing the drive axle, and various smaller components affected by wear over time. Additionally, a wheel alignment was performed, along with some interior fixes.

To conclude, we now present a spotless condition 599 GTB benefitting from huge recent maintenance and a retrofitted HGTE package. Included in sale is the service book, English and Italian owner’s manual, ‘VIP’ folder containing photographs of the manufacturing process and various invoices.
